title: Total United States vehicles entering in Canada 2018
summary: This graph shows the Number of vehicles entering the United States in 2018 .
The Number of cars entering is about 700000 at the start and end of the year .
gold: The displayed chart shows the total number of vehicles entering Canada during 2018 . It 's possible to see how the highest values have been recorded during the spring and summer months . In particular , the maximum number of cars entering Canada has been reached July and a August .
